{"tid":341500,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 根據內容搵首歌","createTime":"2017-07-30T21:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T02:48:53.000Z","uid":108912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f808b45f66fd4ca1467172c9b1f6267eceb80b2","tid":341500,"uid":108912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:06:47.000Z","msg":"本人最近做緊一啲創作，需要有歌曲配合<br />\n但奈何我認識嘅歌曲真係唔多，一時之間搵唔到一首歌嘅歌詞可以配合到創作內容<br />\n所以想集思廣益下求大家幫下忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想搵一首歌，廣東話普通話英文都得，歌詞要配合到以下內容:<br />\na好喜歡b，但奈何b已經有另外喜歡嘅對象<br />\n到最後ab都一齊到(呢個有冇都得，有就最好)<br />\n<br />\n諗到有咩歌配合到就留下歌名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37f4174bc4d3ccbe27fd864e67bf9ff751da384","tid":341500,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:10:39.000Z","msg":"流水很清楚惜花這個責任 真的身份不過送運"},{"pid":"eda5b4dc9e90dd87050cf52059af45ac5537b490","tid":341500,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:20:14.000Z","msg":"勉強幸福 林宥嘉"},{"pid":"80305e998f6e441ce04635a2ab3f9cb0d44df8a5","tid":341500,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:26:25.000Z","msg":"katrina 陳奕迅"},{"pid":"a5627b79202d3753beb4e3cdd577dc159653f8a2","tid":341500,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T21:37:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tLDk2DueeMI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtLDk2DueeMI&d=dGuZikqhVjJsCjegsLqG30kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=18c32baf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tLDk2DueeMI</a>"},{"pid":"2e17952c518c06c0812af7fc4168af3c71a2980e","tid":341500,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T23:14:43.000Z","msg":"張氏情歌"},{"pid":"89e593cf967c43fc333c72b7db135c575c3dfe92","tid":341500,"uid":108912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:38:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/ass